Im die inside if i see a "Rated pg-13" superstar shirt for edge.

WWE probably will drop the ball on this. Let me give the WWE ideas. "Ultimate opportunist" edge has crossed over. He has the fans respect. If he beat up john cena hulk hogan and flair he would still get cheers. because fans respect his works and his come back.
Christian, lita even Matt Hardy. So much past story lines could be throw into todays mixes. Cheap for WWE and a must watch for fans. (no one ever thought Matt was going to delete anyone). Lita going heal with Christian would be a nice swerve to give Edge a break from TV.
New talent. Sure you want to put over new talent, but the WWE will do it in the worst ways. This scares me the worst. Dont treat him as a jobber. No he dont have to be the next BIG things. But he is still a big thing and deserves better.
Double his pay, because the WWE needs him more than ever. Play it right and he could have a long run. get Ron Simmons back on TV. I want my "Damn" shirt. Him and Christian are doing Galaxy cons. If WWE cant afford to steal them part time from there. They suck.

Biggest issue with WWE is talking. People cant sale themselves with their face (see edge montages) if they are trying to remember scripts. Im die inside if i see a "Rated pg-13" superstar shirt for edge.
